name: ICAN
description: ICAN (iCan Token) is a decentralized digital asset built on the Binance Smart Chain (BEP-20 standard). It aims to create a global Web3 financial ecosystem that integrates crypto exchange, credit card payments, DeFi wealth management, and RWA tokenization of real-world businesses.The vision of ICAN is to empower token value through real, sustainable business models, making it the core token of a global Web3 launch platform for enterprises.
